cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.NE 

The paper discusses the use of Deep Learning algorithms for accurate fruit yield estimation from smartphone cameras, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The adaptation of these algorithms for precision agriculture also involves artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and information retrieval (cs.IR) techniques. Additionally, the use of neural networks for fruit yield estimation falls under the neural networks (cs.NE) sub-category.
